marker.placeholder: index:(req,res,next)-> offset = if +req.query.offset > 0 then +req.query.offset * c.snippet_per_page else 0 c.Snippet.listAll(undefined,c.snippet_per_page,offset) .then((snippets)->res.render('index',{offset:+req.query.offset||0,snippets,item_per_page:c.snippet_per_page,item_count:snippets.length,route:'home'})) .catch next...
